DESIGN
Programming language :Python
Classes:  novel , dissociation_press
Methods:  main_method, generate_novel_object

Procedure:

1 In the generate_novel_object function,  a class novel oject is created to contain trigram list of novel ,words and wordsize 	of the novel
	
2 Then the novel object is passed to the dissociation press object which runs dissociation press algorithm on it
  to generate the short story





DEPENDENCIES

The text file of "Christmas Carol" is attached with code
Standard libraries used 

Usage
place the novel file and the python code in the same directory and run the code



